國國內的蒙古少數族裔，甚至在法國的展覽籌備工作都受影響，包括中國要求展覽禁用部分詞彙如「成吉思汗」、「帝國」、以及「蒙古語」等。之後，中國當局甚至要求對展覽的文字、地圖、目錄、通訊資料等有控制權。館方指，北京當局已經對展覽內容全面審查，加入大量偏頗的觀點，目的是為了滿足政權需要。<br />\n<br />\n館方說，與多名歷史學家和專家商討後，為了維護人文、科學和倫理價值，決定即時暫停展覽籌備工作。館方並指，新的展覽會收集歐洲和美國館藏，期望能夠保留展覽的精髓。</strong>"},{"pid":"5b9cb6e533e82125aa2ecf7d88be4c7cecd8bfcf","tid":2241062,"uid":89683,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"點解法國要理支那講嘢？"},{"pid":"b296b4e598d6ff86721ebf510d89639d59146cb3","tid":2241062,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"成吉思汗、蒙古帝國既歷史都要被共產黨否定<br />\n仲有幾多個時期可以用？不如中史將1949前全部用Dark Age概括曬算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22101d1eec975bbb62ce42655fb7f647a8f6d8a5","tid":2241062,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5b9cb6e533e82125aa2ecf7d88be4c7cecd8bfcf","tid":2241062,"uid":89683,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"點解法國要理支那講嘢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"奶共囉，你竟然唔知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fab937aeacaa968e36b8d5eac64b92e1d77295e","tid":2241062,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"林子祥成吉思汗禁唔禁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc49bae8a730b1879fa812c61ebcf5864a3d80a","tid":2241062,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b9cb6e533e82125aa2ecf7d88be4c7cecd8bfcf","tid":2241062,"uid":89683,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"點解法國要理支那講嘢？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:34:39.000Z","msg":"係同「內」蒙古合辦"},{"pid":"eb952704fcd1431ea4c7d9c583f1d5a3b1ac3457","tid":2241062,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,